Program: Outlook
Title: A Spy for Britain in the IRA
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsgf
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The story of Kevin Fulton who claims to have been a British agent in the IRA during The Troubles in the 1970s. Also in the programme: How the Venkateswara Temple, Tirumala in southern India is creating an income from pilgrims' hair. Women's fears as the Taliban's Department for the Promotion of Virtue and Prevention of Vice is to be revived in Afghanistan. Presenter: Frederic Dove. Show less